title: Patriots’ playoff push begins tonight
text:
Baytown Sun photo by Amy Epperson Crunch time 
Goose Creek Memorial freshman football player Alonzo Irving carries the ball down the field during the football game against Vidor at GCM on Wednesday. The Patriots lost 32-0. Posted: Thursday, October 15, 2015 12:00 am Patriots’ playoff push begins tonight By Trent Padgett trent.padgett@baytownsun.com Baytown Sun | 0 comments 
For all intents and purposes, the playoffs start tonight for the Goose Creek Memorial football team.
